-27T04:06:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>飲茶應該係廣州果邊先好過香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你以爲啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e34d0bc38d5ccd7a0e508a350f084e248b119aed","tid":136352,"uid":59459,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-27T04:11:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>飲茶應該係廣州果邊先好過香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你以爲啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n巴打介紹返 遲啲去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"037b330ae2a45660992f2f763a298a4de97e2a20","tid":136352,"uid":2373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-27T04:16:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>飲茶應該係廣州果邊先好過香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你以爲啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n巴打介紹返 遲啲去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n廣州試過兩間一間就好一般不過都差過香港一間直情難食到仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 可能我唔識搵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n中山珠海就好食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 珠海金苑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f6ad27386673eb6e15b2fad2712c109b92e2a5cf","tid":136352,"uid":49643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-27T05:07:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>飲茶應該係廣州果邊先好過香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你以爲啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n巴打介紹返 遲啲去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我返廣州會去「點都得」，但價錢同香港參唔多"},{"pid":"2e740da97873de066da912d94eb7be08943c301a","tid":136352,"uid":41479,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-27T05:10:09.000Z","msg":"丹桂軒"},{"pid":"555327249bfcac4a3708a5a3c651c26389ef6058","tid":136352,"uid":5566,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-27T05:14:02.000Z","msg":"小桃源囉最基本"},{"pid":"4b4c3f0aa3343add9d5652b901340a049d6ad323","tid":136352,"uid":56999,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-27T05:14:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>飲茶應該係廣州果邊先好過香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你以爲啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n大陸大間個d酒樓<br />\n點心有水準<br />\n<br />\n不如果唔隱定<br />\n有d頭2次去唔錯<br />\n再去差左<br />\n唔知係咪轉左㕑"},{"pid":"2c1069cefa8cec5d7263c64283215132d2cb48db","tid":136352,"uid":4635,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-27T05:23:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>飲茶應該係廣州果邊先好過香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你以爲啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n巴打介紹返 遲啲去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我返廣州會去「點都得」，但價錢同香港參唔多</blockquote><br />\n點都德華強果邊都有一間<br />\n都係新派點心酒樓, 用料算足, 價錢唔算平<br />\n<br />\n老派果D就上廣州酒家果D"},{"pid":"38f857820f902485ca25f844a8d65bc415bf1fba","tid":136352,"uid":38860,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-27T14:14:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>小桃源囉最基本</blockquote><br />\n <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}